      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore without feeling like i'm suffocating. everything is just... breaking. the climate, the politics, the way the world is just spinning towards a cliff. i feel like i'm mourning a future that isn't even gone yet, but we know it's coming. what's even the point of trying to build a life or a career when the foundation is literally rotting? it feels so pointless to even exist in this timeline.",
